  "description": "Variation of condition 2 (approved plans) of planning permission 2018/3183 dated 30/08/2019 for&nbsp;Erection of part two-storey, part three-storey building to rear at lower ground floor level [following demolition of existing single storey rear extension at ground floor level]; excavation of enlarged front and rear lightwells; erection of front roof extension and rooflights; landscaping to include platform lift to side and amenity spaces to rear; erection of cycle and refuse stores to the forecourt; to facilitate the change of use from hotel (Use Class C1) to eight separate residential units (Use Class C3).&nbsp;Variation includes reduction in size of front lightwells, relocation of platform lift to rear garden with side access and front gate, layout alteration to flat A, retention of rear lean-to, change in partition to flat D,&nbsp; change of materials from zinc to painted render for front dormer, relocation of rooflight to rear roofslope and relocation of cycle storage",
